item.title: Death's Detective
item.description: Synopsis Death and the Devil’s Daughter have to investigate a death before it even happens. Their search brings them from the cozy depts of hell to the seedy underbelly of a local baking club. Genres Fantasy, Mystery, Humorous, Short Story Downloads Via Kobo

item.title: About
